Author: blocktradecapital
Title: [ANN/ICO]JOHN MCAFEE'S CHOICE FOR THE FUTURE OF HEALTHCARE BLOCKCHAINS.DOCADEMIC
Body: I messaged Charles earlier today, and I look forward to talking with him further on the phone about some ideas.  Docademic has posted the #2 highest investment returns of all the 318 ICO’s completed in 2018 that I counted. Yes, #2 out of 318…. incredible. Other projects should be studying Docademic as a template for how to achieve post-ICO success. And they only raised $1.1 million during the ICO, so again, there just doesn’t seem to be a correlation between the amount of money raised for project (i.e. the hype it generates during the ICO) and the long-term investment success it has. Plus, the project's in Mexico City, far from being a crypto hotspot. Docademic's success has been 100% credited to them putting together a successful entirely campaign on their own.  On the downside, this coin tends to have high amounts of volatility to it. To a certain extent though this is expected with any coin that's risen so much and performed so well.  That being said, the future potential of this coin is still huge, and it continues to resonate with all sorts of people in the crypto space -- traders, influencers, exchanges, P/R firms, media publications. I think just a little more regular communication (i.e. weekly phone calls) between the team and key partners and investors is key. The team could also benefit from more of an in-person presence at conferences and other events, as many conferences are devoting multiple panels to healthcare on the blockchain. Plus, conferences are the perfect medium to do live demos of the app for people, and the fact that this app is something that can be easily comprehended in a quick 5 second demo is hugely advantageous. Not many blockchain projects are like this.  I look forward to talking with Charles and the team further!

Adding larger exchanges spread over a few years is a much better plan. Whoever has been a loyal holder and believed in this project has been rewarded with this. They also did not make tens of millions of dollars in money with the ICO to buy themselves anywhere. Because they still have to prove themselves in the long term. In the long term they can then come up on exchanges much cheaper and even free when the trade volume is big enough and there is enough enthusiasm for it.

Author: Vit83
Title: [ANN/ICO]JOHN MCAFEE'S CHOICE FOR THE FUTURE OF HEALTHCARE BLOCKCHAINS.DOCADEMIC
Body: Few pages ago they said that this will be some kind of airdrop for token holders. Unsold tokens will be given to token holders.   MSG FROM THE CEO CHARLES NADER .  For the past month we have been deliberating what option is best for token holders in regard to unsold tokens. We have come to the following conclusion. We will be burning 150,000,000 tokens and doing a controlled distribution of a little over 123 million tokens to wallets that purchased MTC every month. This will leave the same amount of tokens in the public relative to the team tokens. This is important to provide a balance in tokens between the company and the public. This will also increase the tokens value and will provide incentive for more buyers to acquire MTC every month so they can benefit from the soon to be launched Docademic marketplace as well as the Docademic loan program to qualified doctors. We are very grateful for the involvement of all of you in making our decision. We expect this decision to net positive results short and long term to all token holders present and future. We are awaiting our listing on HItBTC very soon as well as other exchanges. We are in the waiting process of most of the top 10 exchanges on coinmarketcap and will be updating everyone as we get on more. Thank you once again for all your support and insights. We know that our vision to the universalization of medicine and free basic healthcare for the world will speed up as we increase our functionality and expand in the coming months and are very happy to be on this journey with all of you.

Their niche is in addressing issues to do with access to healthcare and to achieve that the company is utilising the blockchain. Docademic believe in a world where everyone has access to quality healthcare, not only the privileged few. Title: [ANN/ICO]JOHN MCAFEE'S CHOICE FOR THE FUTURE OF HEALTHCARE BLOCKCHAINS.DOCADEMIC
Body: Im interested in this project but like many other ico's there are definitely questions. How many users do you have on the app store and the google play store i've yet to be able to fine that? **please if anything will u confirm if your token is an equity, utility, or a security token? it sounds exactly like a utility token which is pretty scary to invest in a utility token in crowdfund stages. Then again its an interesting project with "advisors" like john mccafee on his team with everything about docademics all over the internet anything that has to do with it you will see john mccaffee prefers there service and supports them which also sounds like a classic promoting pump and dump with one of the industries most influential voices. Then again they do have an impressive team of developers but pleas will youanswer how successful this service was in the other "20 countries" its offered in. everything i read says its a "proven" or "successful" method in over 20 countries but no numbers were given, like how many users in these other countries? how many doctors,hospitals,institutions use your services in these countries and how much of a successful app are you at this point especially before these tokens start being used on there? when will you guys hit major exchange markets? This is an impressive squad and voice behind it and interesting project that makes me want to consider getting in on the crowdsale but will someone from docademics please answers these simple questions they very straightforward and if it was as proven as u say it is you would think things like that would already be on your website.

Author: Docademic
Title: [ANN/ICO]JOHN MCAFEE'S CHOICE FOR THE FUTURE OF HEALTHCARE BLOCKCHAINS.DOCADEMIC
Body: ANNOUNCEMENT FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE Docademic to revolutionize Genomics research with Blockchain integration. Launch of Docademic’s MTC 50% bonus Pre-sale will start on February 5TH and last only 4 days.  MEXICO CITY (February 03, 2018) – The countdown is underway for Docademic’s Initial Coin Offering (ICO) Presale, to fund expansion of its Telemedicine services, and for its deal with “HealthSearch Diagnostics” which has genomic testing laboratories to also add patient’s Genomic information on the blockchain.  The ICO Presale, with a limited supply of tokens, will go live on February 5th at 00:00 CST.  Docademic are pioneers of Free basic healthcare using Telemedicine, real doctors and artificial intelligence. Currently Docademic has patients in 20 countries across the globe that can access this service by the press of a button to talk to a doctor face to face on their app for Free. Due to Docademic’s free access for patients it was logical to add to their already growing database that is going on a blockchain, Genomic information.  Docademic patient identities will not only have their health records that start with Docademics free telemedicine service, they will also be able to add Genomic information. This will revolutionize the future of clinical research, for example determining if patients have specific cancer genes just by accessing information on the blockchain. No other company in the world has access to so many patients across multiple countries. Patients will receive a home genome extraction sample kit where they will be able to send back their samples to get tested and results will be uploaded to their patient IDs on the blockchain along with their other medical data. First batches of patient genomic data are estimated to be uploaded to the blockchain within the next 6 months.  The company’s use of block chain technology has completely revolutionized its operations. Blockchain transactions are jointly processed by a mass of computers known as nodes. It is dynamic system which guarantees that the network is not controlled by any single source. The success of the ICO will enable Docademic to implement a blockchain powered by MTC. Their use of the Second generation blockchain Ethereum goes beyond exchanging digital currency and can operate entire applications. This will further mobilize the efficiency of the Medical platform as well as add access to anonymized patient data including genetic information using the MTC token.  Their Token sale structure is very attractive for contributors. A limited supply of tokens will be sold at a 50% bonus for only 4 days. The bonus drops to 40%, 30% and 20% until the presale ends on the 28th of February or the limited presale token supply is sold out. Whichever occurs first. The Soft cap is 525 ETH and Hard Cap for the Presale is 2,100 ETH. The tokens low price of .000035 ETH, about 3 cents USD, and its limited supply of tokens in its presale will make the token sale of high demand for buyers. After the Presale ends a Retail sale without bonuses will be launched 20 days after with a token supply 5 times larger. The retail crowd sale will have a Token supply equivalent to 10,150 ETH. Hard Cap for the complete ICO including the Presale and crowd sale is 12,250 ETH. This means that the presale will offer less than 20% of the available tokens and provides scarcity at the bonus offered. The token will be listed on many crypto currency exchanges as soon as possible after the ICO ends.  “We already have Governments and Healthcare institutions as clients that will use the MTC token for their own upcoming and existing medical services, as they migrate to decentralized platforms, said Co-founder and CEO Charles Nader. “We envision MTC will be used in the broader healthcare industry and any other industries for various purposes including using the data we generate daily for different healthcare applications including Genomic analysis.  The MTC token is the exclusive medium to access data generated by Docademic's services including patient healthcare and genomic Data”.”  Docademic’s ICO boasts an ICO profile of 3.9 on ICO Bench, an ICO rating platform supported by experts.  How to participate in the ICO sale Contributors can participate by visiting https://ico.docademic.com/ where they will have the option of buying the MTC token on February 5th at 00:00 CST. Buyers are encouraged to act fast and benefit from a 50% discount from a limited supply of tokens when they purchase between February 5th and February 8th. For further details, visit: https://ico.docademic.com/, read the Whitepaper and follow Docademic on social network Telegram, Facebook and Twitter.            Contact Info Name: Charles Nader Email: Info@docademic.com Organization: Docademic Address: Mexico Phone: (52) 55-68230210

Title: [ANN/ICO]JOHN MCAFEE'S CHOICE FOR THE FUTURE OF HEALTHCARE BLOCKCHAINS.DOCADEMIC

If a patients needs his/her doctor to see their specific data from the blockchain then the blockchain asks that patient for permision and the patient must grant access by submiting their private key. This is the only way you can view specific information about an individual.

Author: Docademic
Title: [ANN/ICO]JOHN MCAFEE'S CHOICE FOR THE FUTURE OF HEALTHCARE BLOCKCHAINS.DOCADEMIC
Body: We believe it will be. Thats why we started this. Plus with the combination of Blockchain and Artificial intelligence we can transform healthcare in the world.  Ill give you an example of a case we had just today.  This morning a woman called in requesting medical assistance. She was pregnant. She decided to self medicate her pain without knowing that the medication she took could put her at risk of causing an abortion. Luckily one of our Doctors, Dr Lizbeth Martinez, guided her to the correct treatment and a life was posibly saved by the service.  Many people use our service every day. They are all in shock we offer it. We are extremely proud to be doing this and to have invented this free service - business model. Saving peoples lives and being able to sustain it through a great business mode, its the best way to spend our time in life as the creators in this culture changing project.

Author: Docademic
Title: [ANN/ICO]JOHN MCAFEE'S CHOICE FOR THE FUTURE OF HEALTHCARE BLOCKCHAINS.DOCADEMIC
Body: No, we have Doctors on call 24/7 in three shifts. They all work full time at Docademic. Anyone can download our app, register, press a button and talk to a Doctor 24/7 for free. It doesnt matter how long it takes. If we cant solve the problem through Telemedicine we reffer you to the best hospital or doctor in your area. Our focus is in offering the best service available.
